## OS Guardrails

Use the `os-guardrails` workflow for any OS-level security or workstation hardening task.

### Guardrail Constraints
Never propose or apply the following unless the user explicitly requests the exact item: `linux-hardened`, kernel lockdown mode, `module.sig_enforce=1`, `hidepid=2` on `/proc`, `hardened_malloc` preload, AppArmor/SELinux rollout, LKRG.

